```

### Learning Chunk 5H: Advanced Deployment Scenarios

```bash
echo ""
echo "=== Advanced Deployment Scenarios ==="
echo "üéì REAL-WORLD DEPLOYMENT PATTERNS:"
echo "‚Ä¢ Custom environment variables"
echo "‚Ä¢ Volume mounting for persistent data"
echo "‚Ä¢ Network configuration"
echo "‚Ä¢ Health checks and monitoring"

echo ""
echo "üìã Scenario 1: Custom Environment Configuration"
# Run with environment variables
docker run -d -p 8081:80 \
  --name webapp-custom \
  -e NGINX_HOST=localhost \
  -e NGINX_PORT=80 \
  ${DOCKER_USERNAME}/mywebapp:latest

echo "‚úÖ Started webapp-custom with environment variables"
```

### Learning Chunk 5I: Volume Mounting Scenario

```bash
echo ""
echo "=== Volume Mounting for Custom Content ==="
echo "üìÅ Scenario 2: Adding custom content via volumes"
echo "This simulates mounting configuration or dynamic content"

# Create custom content
mkdir -p custom-content
echo "<h1>Custom Content</h1><p>This content is mounted from the host!</p>" > custom-content/custom.html

echo "‚úÖ Created custom content directory"

# Run with volume
docker run -d -p 8082:80 \
  --name webapp-volume \
  -v $(pwd)/custom-content:/usr/share/nginx/html/custom \
  ${DOCKER_USERNAME}/mywebapp:latest

echo "‚úÖ Started webapp-volume with custom content mounted"
echo "üåê Custom content will be available at /custom/custom.html"
```

### Learning Chunk 5J: Test All Deployments

```bash
echo ""
echo "=== Testing All Deployment Scenarios ==="

# Test original deployment
echo "üß™ Testing original deployment (port 8080):"
curl -s http://localhost:8080 | grep -o "<title>.*</title>" && echo "‚úÖ Original deployment working"

echo ""
# Test custom deployment
echo "üß™ Testing custom environment deployment (port 8081):"
curl -I http://localhost:8081 | head -1

echo ""
# Test volume deployment
echo "üß™ Testing volume mounted deployment (port 8082):"
curl -s http://localhost:8082/custom/custom.html | grep "Custom Content" && echo "‚úÖ Volume mounting working" || echo "‚ö†Ô∏è Volume test - check custom content"

echo ""
echo "üìä All running containers:"
docker ps --format "table {{.Names}}\t{{.Ports}}\t{{.Status}}"
```

